ACADEMIC FREE LICENSE (Limited Period: 2024 – 2027)
================================================================================

During the period of January 1, 2024 through December 31, 2030, LADOCK Desktop
is made available FREE OF CHARGE exclusively to eligible academic users under
the following conditions:

ELIGIBILITY
  You qualify for the free academic license if:
  - You are affiliated with a recognized university or academic research
    institution, AND
  - You access LADOCK using a verified institutional email address
    (e.g., .ac.id, .edu, .ac.uk, or equivalent national academic domain), AND
  - Your use of LADOCK is solely for non-commercial academic research,
    teaching, or educational purposes.

ACADEMIC LICENSE TERMS
  - You may install and use LADOCK on institutional machines for academic work.
  - You may share LADOCK with colleagues at the same institution.
  - You must cite the relevant LADOCK publications in any work that uses
    LADOCK (see CITATION section below).
  - You may NOT use LADOCK for any commercial purpose under this license.
  - You may NOT sublicense, sell, or redistribute LADOCK.

AFTER DECEMBER 31, 2030
  The free academic license period ends. Academic users will be eligible for
  a discounted institutional license. Contact the licensor for current
  academic pricing and renewal terms.

