COMMERCIAL LICENSE
================================================================================

Any use of LADOCK Desktop by a for-profit company, contract research
organization (CRO), pharmaceutical company, biotechnology firm, or any entity
using LADOCK for commercial purposes requires a COMMERCIAL LICENSE, regardless
of the date.

Commercial use includes but is not limited to:
  - Drug discovery or lead optimization for commercial products
  - Providing docking services to paying clients
  - Integrating LADOCK into a commercial software product or pipeline
  - Internal R&D within a for-profit organization

